Class TimeableAspect

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ametiste.metrics.aop.TimeableAspect

  • public class TimeableAspect
extends java.lang.Object
    Aspect for registration of method execution time for methods that annotated with Timeable annotation. Increments metric with identifier, resolved from Timeable.name() and Timeable.nameSuffixExpression() for value
